*****
[4] UK
Date: Fri 3 Jun 2011
Source: BBC [edited]
http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-13642380


The Health Protection Agency has announced 4 more cases of _E. coli_
infection in the UK linked to the outbreak in Germany. It brings the
total number of British cases to 11, with all those affected having
recently traveled to Germany. The HPA said there was no evidence of it
being passed from person to person in the UK.

